author: National Geographic
description:
On their journey through Italy's Emilia-Romagna region, Antoni Porowski and Justin Theroux sample freshly made tortelli con la coda and discover the simplistic beauty of the local delicacies.

No Taste Like Home with Antoni Porowski is now streaming on Disney+.
title: Never underestimate the power of food to spark emotion #NoTasteLikeHomewithAntoniPorowski
